"PHP: Hypertext Preprocessor"
PHP is a widely-used, open source scripting language
executed on the server (server side language)


//////PHP Syntax///////
1. 
    <?php
      // PHP code write here
    ?> 

2. <?php
      echo "Hello From PHP";
    ?>
3. 
    {{$variablename}}    //to display data
    or
    echo $variablename;
 
 
 /////Example////////////////////////////
 
  <!DOCTYPE html>
  <html>
  <body>

    <h1>My first PHP page</h1>

    <?php
      echo "Hello World!";
    ?>

  </body>
  </html> 
